<p><strong>Office of Undergraduate Admissions</strong><br />
	Limited Enrollment Programs<br />
	Website: <a href="http://www.lep.umd.edu/" target="_blank">http://www.lep.umd.edu/</a><br />
	E-mail: <a href="mailto:lep@umd.edu">lep@umd.edu</a><br /><br /><strong>Clark School Undergraduate Advising</strong><br />
	Website: <a href="https://eng.umd.edu/undergraduate-transfer-admission" target="_blank">https://eng.umd.edu/undergraduate-transfer-admission</a><br />
	E-mail: <a href="mailto:transfer_engr@umd.edu">transfer_engr@umd.edu</a><br /><br /><strong>Transfer Credit Information</strong><br />
	The Transfer Credit Services (TCS) at the University of Maryland can provide students with information on courses that can transfer to UMD.  Through the TCS, students can also submit course syllabi for evaluation of courses that do not currently transfer to our institution.</p>
<p><strong>The Transfer Credit Services</strong><br />
	Website: <a href="http://transfercredit.umd.edu/" target="_blank">http://transfercredit.umd.edu/</a><br />
	E-mail: <a href="mailto:transfercredit@umd.edu">transfercredit@umd.edu</a><br />
	 </p>
<h3>
	Pre-Transfer Advising</h3>
<p>The Pre-Transfer Advising Office at the University provides support to prospective transfer students. Pre-Transfer Advisors help students determine how previous coursework will apply to University of Maryland degrees, identify remaining general education and major requirements, and estimate time to degree.</p>
<p><strong>Pre-Transfer Advising Office</strong><br />
	Website: <a href="http://www.pretransferadvising.umd.edu/" target="_blank">http://www.pretransferadvising.umd.edu/</a><br />
	E-mail: <a href="mailto:transferadvising@umd.edu">transferadvising@umd.edu</a></p>
<p> </p>
